headline: Why IQVIA (IQV) Stock Is Up Today

headline: IQV Q2 Deep Dive: AI Initiatives and Pipeline Growth Drive Outperformance Amid Margin Pressures
summary: Clinical research company IQVIA (NYSE: IQV) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 5.3% year on year to $4.02 billion. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $16.2 billion at the midpoint came in 0.8% above analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.81 per share was 1.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
